<i>You still there?</i>

37
00:01:53.480 --> 00:01:54.749
-Yeah--
- <i>Sorry to interrupt.</i>

38
00:01:54.916 --> 00:01:56.684
<i>I hear the Brauns throw</i>
<i>a notorious party.</i>

39
00:01:56.851 --> 00:01:58.352
