<i>you're a fan.</i>

43
00:02:03.390 --> 00:02:05.994
<i>so I thought I'd wish you</i>
<i>a happy birthday.</i>

44
00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:07.361
<i>see how you're doing.</i>

45
00:02:07.528 --> 00:02:09.564
<i>Have fun. Ally.</i>
<i>but not too much fun.</i>

46
00:02:09.731 --> 00:02:10.665
